title: Mike Stuart Span - Children Of Tomorrow (2011) (mp3, 320 kbps)
description:
Mike Stuart Span - "Children Of Tomorrow"  [mp3, 320 kbps]

includes cover scans and complete CD booklet notes.

 (1,2) A & B sides of Columbia single, November 1966
